Option Buying Power: {{OPTION_BUYING_POWER}}
Margin Equity %: {{MARGIN_EQUITY_PERCENTAGE}}
Account Constraints:
{{ACCOUNT_CONSTRAINTS}}
Options Chain (may be empty):
{{OPTIONS_CHAIN}}

Message to parse (this is the only message you should parse):
"{{MESSAGE_TEXT}}"

Output discipline:
- Return only valid JSON.
- No markdown fences.
- No extra commentary outside JSON.

Contract examples (signals only):

Example A (mixed stock + options):
Message: `Added stock at $13.95 and some $12.5C for March at $1.75 avg just to add some juice. 4.5% weighting.`
Output shape excerpt (full output must still include immutable top-level contract keys):
{
  "signals": [
    {
      "ticker": "GLDD",
      "action": "BUY",
      "weight_percent": 4.5,
      "vehicles": [
        {"type":"STOCK","intent":"EXECUTE","side":"BUY","enabled":true,"option_type":null,"strike":null,"expiry":null,"quantity_hint":null},
        {"type":"OPTION","intent":"EXECUTE","side":"BUY","enabled":true,"option_type":"CALL","strike":12.5,"expiry":"March","quantity_hint":null}
      ]
    }
  ]
}

Example B (options only):
Message: `Added AAPL $200C for March 2026, small speculative options position only.`
Output shape excerpt (full output must still include immutable top-level contract keys):
{
  "signals": [
    {
      "ticker":"AAPL",
      "action":"BUY",
      "vehicles":[
        {"type":"OPTION","intent":"EXECUTE","side":"BUY","enabled":true,"option_type":"CALL","strike":200,"expiry":"March 2026","quantity_hint":null}
      ]
    }
  ]
}
